name: Walk to George's
description:
Made in 5 hours as part of Blue Light Collective's #bytesizedjam.
A Game about walking to my partners house and listening to music.

Song Lyrics List:

1. Postcodes - Verge Collection
2. How to socialise and make friends - Camp Cope
3. Smogged Out - Skegss
4. Girly Bits - Ali Barter
5. I Haven't been taking care of myself - Alex Lahey
6. Two Angles - Daffodils

All the above music are Australian & NZ artists and you should check all of em out!
